O:a) "\\(\\cos \\theta\\)", b) "\\(-\\cos \\theta\\)", c) "\\(\\tan \\theta\\)", d) "\\(\\sin \\theta\\)"
R:"In the second quadrant, sine is positive. \\(\\sin(180^\\circ - \\theta) = \\sin \\theta\\)."
}

q {
