q {
Q:"\\(R =\\)"
A:"d"
O:a) "\\(\\frac{a}{2\\sin\\gamma}\\)", b) "\\(\\frac{a}{2\\sin\\beta}\\)", c) "\\(\\frac{c}{2\\sin\\gamma}\\)", d) "\\(\\frac{a}{2\\sin\\alpha}\\)"
R:"Sine rule: \\(\\frac{a}{\\sin\\alpha} = 2R \\Rightarrow R = \\frac{a}{2\\sin\\alpha}\\)."
